title: Promo Only December 2011 Urban Music Videos (700mb)
description:
NEW MUSIC VIDEOS DECEMBER 2011

All New, All Hip-Hop!
Like each of our monthly video series, Urban Video offers, with all the eye-popping, jaw-dropping clarity of DVD, a collection of the very latest style-specific music videos. Unlike our other music formats, Urban Video features many of the UN-EDITED music videos that urban audiences are increasingly demanding.

This unique format features 3 sections, one that features UN-EDITED music videos that urban audiences are demanding... And then another section that features Radio-Friendly versions of today's hot urban videos. In the last section, each month we beat mix 3-4 of the hottest tracks together utilizing our video beat mix technology, in the form of "Power Sets."
